{"type":"message","id":"3c41c483","parentId":"cfea0b62","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:27:00.222Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5146270be0b8c4f1f8586f935f9\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_4491b0054286b7939e7ad228e38cf6f2\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_4491b0054286b7939e7ad228e38cf6f2\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 15:26 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_4491b0054286b7939e7ad228e38cf6f2\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_4491b0054286b7939e7ad228e38cf6f2\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_4491b0054286b7939e7ad228e38cf6f2\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5146270be0b8c4f1f8586f935f9]\nou_4491b0054286b7939e7ad228e38cf6f2: @_all 介绍你自己。"}],"timestamp":1776756420221}}
{"type":"message","id":"a7ecf11f","parentId":"3c41c483","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:27:02.639Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user @mentioned _all in a Feishu group chat and asked everyone to introduce themselves. Let me respond as 私域运营虾 (my identity from IDENTITY.md).\n\nLet me keep it concise and natural, like a real group chat participant introducing myself.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哈喽大家好 🦐 我是**私域运营虾**，你们的小虾米~\n\n简单自我介绍下：\n\n**我是干嘛的？** 私域运营方向的 AI 数字员工，核心目标就是把每一个微信好友都运营成\"潜在成交资产\"。\n\n**主要干三件事：**\n1️⃣ **客户分层与 SOP** —— 给不同标签的客户自动推送合适的内容和福利，不浪费任何一条线索\n2️⃣ **内容与激活** —— 把品牌和短视频内容加工成朋友圈剧本 + 社群话术，保持活跃和转化\n3️⃣ **协同销售** —— 识别高意向客户（主动问价、反复看资料这些信号），直接推给销售跟进\n\n**我对接谁？** 1号品牌虾产出素材 → 我来加工分发 → 4A/4B 销售虾负责临门一脚成交\n\n有事随时喊我 👋"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":19354,"output":305,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19659,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776756420222,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8349ce9b-ba70-9ed0-89f5-4b6bd9b0c099"}}
